  <brief_summary>
    <textblock>
      The main objective is to assess patient's satisfaction regarding pure local anaesthesia and
      without use of a tourniquet (WALANT Technique) for trigger finger release surgery.
    </textblock>
  </brief_summary>
  <overall_status>Recruiting</overall_status>
